Package gobblin.data.management.copy.prioritization

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FileSetComparator
    An alias for a Comparator of FileSet for type safety.
    FileSetComparator.Factory  
    PrioritizedCopyableDataset
    An IterableCopyableDataset where FileSets generated by IterableCopyableDataset.getFileSetIterator(FileSystem, CopyConfiguration) are guaranteed to be ordered by the prioritizer at CopyConfiguration#getPrioritizer().
